    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for anyone looking for a functional daily driver. Mechanically, the engine and transmission are in good working order and the car drives smoothly. However, please be aware that there are visible signs of wear, including some minor exterior scratches and dings, as well as some fading in the interior upholstery. All major systems are operational, but some minor features like the rear window motor may require attention soon. It\u2019s a solid, honest car for someone prioritizing utility over aesthetics.",
