      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is an exemplary specimen of automotive engineering, maintained in impeccable condition. This vehicle transcends the standard pre-owned experience, offering a pristine aesthetic and mechanical integrity that mirrors its original delivery state. Every detail, from the flawless coachwork to the meticulously preserved interior, has been curated for the most demanding enthusiast. This is an invitation to acquire a vehicle of uncompromising quality and investment-grade preservation.",
      "price": 48500.0,
